Help Type: command
Command: wikigraph wkg-job://<job-id> pause

Purpose:
  Pause one queued or running job.

Usage:
  wikigraph wkg-job://<job-id> pause

Arguments:
  <job-id>              Full job id or an unambiguous prefix.

Behavior:
  - Paused jobs keep their workspace and are not scheduled.
  - Resume with `wikigraph wkg-job://<job-id> resume`.

Example:
  wikigraph wkg-job://75d12f7e pause
